name: The Elder Salmon (=චᆽච=)
bio: Hey cutie! I'm The Elder Salmon (=චᆽච=). I enjoy sitting on your computer, eating until I loathe myself, and staying woke. Sometimes I daydream of a life full of slappin' da bass, hamburgers, and volunteering at the local kitten rescue shelter. I look forward to picking on mice with you.
